<p><span>报告期内，智洋创新存货金额分别为</span><span>3368.30</span><span>万元、</span><span>5980.98</span><span>万元、</span><span>1.43</span><span>亿元和</span><span>2.20</span><span>亿元，占流动资产比例分别为</span><span>17.10%</span><span>、</span><span>17.73%</span><span>、</span><span>28.48%</span><span>和</span><span>39.15%</span><span>。</span></p>
