<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装主营业务收入分别为<span>2218.04</span>万元、<span>8729.53</span>万元、<span>2.02</span>亿元、<span>7515.00</span>万元；同期主营业务收现比率（销售商品、提供劳务收到的现金<span>/</span>主营业务收入）分别为<span>132.87%</span>、<span>66.07%</span>、<span>78.15%</span>、<span>94.13%</span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="142" src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/c045a371d88c48dcbfbd3da0d23ce02a.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装归母净利润分别为<span>-684.67</span>万元、<span>1729.27</span>万元、<span>4762.51</span>万元、<span>991.31</span>万元，经营活动产生的现金流量净额分别为<span>-3717.21</span>万元、<span>182.14</span>万元、<span>-1587.63</span>万元、<span>-8872.02</span>万元。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="190" src="http://p2.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/3774868f511c483795ebea97367e21e6.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年、<span>2019</span>年、<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装经营活动产生的现金流量净额均为负，<span>2018</span>年，芯碁微装净现比（经营现金流量净额<span>/</span>净利润）为<span>10.53%</span>。</span></p>
<p><strong><span>2020</span><span>年上半年研发费用率<span>26.55%</span></span></strong></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装研发费用分别为<span>791.80</span>万元、<span>1698.10</span>万元、<span>2854.95</span>万元、<span>2015.02</span>万元，占营业收入比例分别为<span>35.70%</span>、<span>19.45%</span>、<span>14.12%</span>、<span>26.55%</span>。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="108" src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/6c80fafb8f204fdcafc10481e124265d.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装研发费用中材料支出分别为<span>331.28</span>万元、<span>696.47</span>万元、<span>1431.97</span>万元、<span>1203.71</span>万元，占比分别为<span>41.84%</span>、<span>41.01%</span>、<span>50.16%</span>、<span>59.74%</span>；职工薪酬分别为<span>419.04</span>万元、<span>557.16</span>万元、<span>810.64</span>万元、<span>642.72</span>万元，占比分别为<span>52.92%</span>、<span>32.81%</span>、<span>28.39%</span>、<span>31.90%</span>。</span></p>
