<p><strong><span>2020</span><span>年上半年总资产<span>5.09</span>亿元 总负债<span>1.62</span>亿元</span></strong></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装资产合计分别为<span>9606.05</span>万元、<span>1.68</span>亿元、<span>4.68</span>亿元、<span>5.09</span>亿元，其中，流动资产分别为<span>7420.69</span>万元、<span>1.47</span>亿元、<span>4.23</span>亿元、<span>4.33</span>亿元，非流动资产分别为<span>2185.36</span>万元、<span>2099.93</span>万元、<span>4506.75</span>万元、<span>7584.70</span>万元。</span></p>
<p><img width="554" height="144" src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201026/830af1ddb27744a0ad1a01083d260fe2.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span>2017</span><span>年至<span>2020</span>年<span>1-6</span>月，芯碁微装负债合计分别为<span>5667.70</span>万元、<span>5541.29</span>万元、<span>1.30</span>亿元、<span>1.62</span>亿元，其中，流动负债分别为<span>5637.53</span>万元、<span>4655.50</span>万元、<span>1.17</span>亿元、<span>1.23</span>亿元，非流动负债分别为<span>30.17</span>万元、<span>885.79</span>万元、<span>1312.84</span>万元、<span>3914.71</span>万元。</span></p>
